{
  "stem": "24195.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So two weeks later, I went back to see somebody else at the paper, same paper.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The man hired me on the spot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He became a lifelong friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's still-- now he's retired.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He's In his 70s.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No he's-- yeah, he's a fellow German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was smart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was back as one of the American officers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a-- came to the US as a 16-year-old in 1938 and studied at Yale.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had relatives here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He's half Jewish, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he's not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He's Catholic, I think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that's-- no, he left, too, because of the persecution.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he came in 1937.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was back as an American officer in a US uniform, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he hired me, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I started working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I worked there for travel all over Germany in a US military car with a German driver, and covering war crime trials, DP camps, anything of, of topics, you know, of events that happened in the post-- my, my beat was, my regular beat was the Bavarian government.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I interviewed the, the Bavarian prime minister, the economics-- that was my regular beat, going around every day and, and, and talking to the newly-formed Bavarian authorities.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were two types, the Nuremberg war crime trials, which was, I think, began in '46.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I did not really go to that trial, but I followed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because one of the Americans, German-Americans on the paper, covered that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was, you know, a, a major thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they sent me to, they sent me to what-- the denazification courts, where Germans judge Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were to make-- to judge their behavior during the Nazi times.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If they had done anything wrong, if they had, you know, acted unethically, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
